We feel powerless (and we are, literally!) but we can always laugh. So, 12 years after South Africans first got load-shat on by Eskom – it’s back, and badder than ever. On Monday, barely minutes after Eskom hit us with stage-6 load-shedding for the first time ever, longsuffering citizens started flooding the interwebs with Eskom memes. You’ve got to laugh, because if you start crying you may never stop.                                   This article first appeared on CapeTalk : 17 funny Eskom memes to help you deal with the tragic absurdity of load shedding